description:
Join us for a week of prayer, April 22 - 25, 2024. Come hear words of inspiration from our student speakers. 

Live streamed nightly at 7:00 p.m. on our YouTube Channel.

Theme: The Sower Went Forth to Sow

A blessing awaits you!
